==Trivia==
*Although the spell "[[Monster Examine]]" claims this monster can be poisoned and venomed, it cannot. This is likely due to the poison/venom timer being used to determine how long the monster should appear for.
*The Zamorak Wizard yells "Die, human!" although it appears to be human as well.

